      • buildMapClickEvent

        public static Hashtable<String,Object> buildMapClickEvent(@NonNull
                                                          Location location,
                                                          @NonNull
                                                          String gestureId,
                                                          double zoom)
        Helper method for tracking gesture events
        Parameters:
        gestureId - Type of Gesture See MapboxEvent#GESTURE_DOUBLETAP MapboxEvent#GESTURE_TWO_FINGER_SINGLETAP MapboxEvent#GESTURE_QUICK_ZOOM MapboxEvent#GESTURE_PAN_START MapboxEvent#GESTURE_PINCH_START MapboxEvent#GESTURE_ROTATION_START MapboxEvent#GESTURE_PITCH_START
        location - Location coordinates at start of gesture
        zoom - Zoom level to be registered
